1. Theoretical models                                             3643 1451
 The POD code is based on the spherical optical model, the        3643 1451
distorted-wave Born approximaiton (DWBA), one-component exciton   3643 1451
preequilibrium model, and the Hauser-Feshbach-Moldauer statis-    3643 1451
tical model.  With the preequilibrim model, semi-empirical        3643 1451
pickup and knockout process can be taken into account for         3643 1451
composite-particle emission.  The gamma-ray emission from the     3643 1451
compound nucleus can be calculated within the framework of the    3643 1451
exciton model.  The code is capable of reading in particle        3643 1451
transmission coefficients calculated by separate spherical or     3643 1451
coupled-channel optical model code.                               3643 1451
